Scorponok


Scorponok smile, "So you will be my Partner, Great." Scorponok was 
ready to jump up and down. "I am honored to have a partner like you." 
Scopronok smile. He was Happy. He couldn't stop smiling at DarkMouse. 
"I would just like to say one thing, you are beautiful," Scorponok 
really meant it. He liked her more then anything, He might even love 
her. Scorponok thought to himself, 'how can this be that I love her,
I 
never loved anyone before.'
